<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-9793386_R-HSA-9793375_controller_BFO_0000051_REACTO_R-HSA-9793384_R-HSA-9793386_R-HSA-9793375_component_Reactome_R-HSA-9793380>
